ContentDesc_Castrum Meridianum - Außenbe: So begins the third phase of Operation Archon, which entails a frontal assault upon Castrum Meridianum, Gaius van Baelsar's seat of power. Forming the main thrust, the Immortal Flames will strike at the stronghold with all their strength, though this is but a feint. While the garrison's eyes are drawn outwards, you and your comrades must steal past its defenses and attempt to deactivate the magitek field which protects the Praetorium, the fortress within a fortress wherein the Ultima Weapon is believed to be housed.
Instancecontenttextdata_3913_Text: You will not take any more from me!
Instancecontenttextdata_3914_Text: The pain I have suffered, I shall visit upon you a hundredfold!
Instancecontenttextdata_33506_Text: This is Cid. To review, our goal is to deactivate the magitek field.
Instancecontenttextdata_33507_Text: If you could create a diversion─that's to say, wreak lots of havoc─I'll search for the field generator.
Instancecontenttextdata_33508_Text: <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>, how are you faring? ...Reached a dead end, you say? I believe I know where you are.
Instancecontenttextdata_33509_Text: There's a disposal chute nearby. Find it and jump in, and you'll emerge in a different sector.
Instancecontenttextdata_33511_Text: I've located the controls for the security system. A moment while I disable the barriers.
Instancecontenttextdata_33512_Text: Another bulkhead, eh? Fortunately I'm equipped for the task. Stand back!
Instancecontenttextdata_33513_Text: Come on, the field generator should be just up ahead!
Instancecontenttextdata_33514_Text: There it is! Keep the enemy occupied while I take it out of commission!
Instancecontenttextdata_33515_Text: You will not take any more from me!
Instancecontenttextdata_33516_Text: The pain I have suffered, I shall visit upon you a hundredfold!
Instancecontenttextdata_33518_Text: Hmph, you're tough, I grant you that.
Instancecontenttextdata_33519_Text: But I will break you soon enough!
Instancecontenttextdata_33520_Text: You will not defeat me! You will not!
Instancecontenttextdata_33521_Text: I'm also pleased to say I've found a suit of armor. Press on─I'll meet you just ahead.
Instancecontenttextdata_33523_Text: We must hold the enemy here! All units─attack!
Instancecontenttextdata_33524_Text: The central crossing is overrun! Requesting immediate reinforcements!
Instancecontenttextdata_33525_Text: Gah, damn these savages! Deploy the reserve colossi!
Instancecontenttextdata_33526_Text: How can this be...? R-Reinforcements! We need more reinforcements!
